'''Hepatitis A''' (si woyɔna tsa be '''infectious hepatitis''') nye [[Acute (medical)|acute]] [[infectious disease]] na [[liver]] tsona hepatitis A virus gbɔ (HAV).<ref name=Sherris>{{cite book | author = Ryan KJ, Ray CG (editors) | title = Sherris Medical Microbiology | edition = 4th | pages = 541–4 | publisher = McGraw Hill | year = 2004 | isbn = 0-8385-8529-9 }}</ref> Dɔa lele geɖe mefia dzesi boo aɖeke o vevietɔ le amesiwo metsi o la me.<ref name=AFP2012/> Ɣeyiɣi tso dɔa ƒe gɔmedzedze yi eƒe dzesiwo gbɔ le ame siwo lenɛ me la le abe kɔsiɖa eve yi ade.<ref name="pmid16271543">{{cite journal| author=Connor BA| title=Hepatitis A vaccine in the last-minute traveler| journal=Am. J. Med.| volume=118 |issue=Suppl 10A| pages=58S–62S| year=2005| pmid=16271543| doi=10.1016/j.amjmed.2005.07.018}}</ref> Ne dzesiwo dze la wonɔa anyi zi geɖe abe kɔsiɖa enyi esiwo nye: trutsɔame, trutru, afɔdzidedɔ, [[jaundice|yellow skin]], fever kple aŋɔmeɖuame.<ref name=AFP2012/> Ame geɖewo abe 10–15% gakpɔa dzesiwo ƒe vava le dzinu ade tso dɔa lele zi gbatɔ megbe.<ref name=AFP2012/> [[Acute liver failure]] teaŋu dzɔna ɣeaɖewoyi vevietɔ le ametsitsiwo me.<ref name=AFP2012/>

<!-- Cause -->
Emama toa nu ɖuɖu alo tsi nono siwo me dɔlekui mi le.<ref name=AFP2012>{{cite journal|last=Matheny|first=SC|last2=Kingery |first2=JE|title=Hepatitis A.|journal=Am Fam Physician |date=1 December 2012|volume=86|issue=11|pages=1027–34; quiz 1010–2|pmid=23198670 |url=http://www.aafp.org/afp/2012/1201/p1027.html}}</ref> [[Shellfish]] si womeɖa nyuie o la etsoƒe bɔbɔtɔ wu.<ref>{{Cite journal  | last1 = Bellou | first1 = M. | last2 = Kokkinos | first2 = P. | last3 = Vantarakis | first3 = A. | title = Shellfish-borne viral outbreaks: a systematic review. | journal = Food Environ Virol | volume = 5 | issue = 1 | pages = 13–23 |date=March 2013 | doi = 10.1007/s12560-012-9097-6 | pmid = 23412719 }}</ref> Woateŋu amae to kadodo kplokpui kple amesi lee la me.<ref name=AFP2012/> Togbɔbe dzesi aɖeke me dzea le ɖeviwo ŋu edziedzi ne woxɔ dɔ sia hã la woateŋu aɖee na amebubuwo.<ref name=AFP2012/> Ne elee zi ɖeka ko magalee le wo agbeme o.<ref>{{cite book|title=The Encyclopedia of Hepatitis and Other Liver Diseases|year=2006|publisher=Infobase |isbn=9780816069903|page=105|url=http://books.google.ca/books?id=HfPU99jIfboC&pg=PA105}}</ref> Dɔlekuia kpɔkpɔ hia ʋu dodo kpɔ elebena eƒe dzesiwo sɔ kple dɔlele bubuwo.<ref name=AFP2012/> Enye [[hepatitis]] virus atɔ siwo wonya: A, [[hepatitis B|B]], [[hepatitis C|C]], [[hepatitis D|D]], kple [[hepatitis E|E]].

<!-- Prevention and Treatment -->
[[hepatitis A vaccine]] la nye mɔxenu nyui.<ref name=AFP2012/><ref name=Irv2012>{{Cite journal  | last1 = Irving | first1 = GJ. | last2 = Holden | first2 = J. | last3 = Yang | first3 = R. | last4 = Pope | first4 = D. | title = Hepatitis A immunisation in persons not previously exposed to hepatitis A. | journal = Cochrane Database Syst Rev | volume = 7 | issue =  | pages = CD009051 | year = 2012 | doi = 10.1002/14651858.CD009051.pub2 | pmid = 22786522 }}</ref> Dukɔ aɖewo ɖoe anyi na ɖeviwo kple ame siwo axɔe bɔbɔe siwo medo abui o.<ref name=AFP2012/><ref name=WHO2013/> Edze abe awɔ dɔ le agbe ŋkekewo katã me.<ref name=AFP2012/> Mɔxenu bubu aɖewoe nye [[hand washing]] kple nu ɖaɖa nyuie.<ref name=AFP2012/> Dɔdada mɔnu tɔxe aɖeke meli o, gbɔɖeme kple atike nono na [[nausea]] alo [[diarrhea]] nyo le ɣeyiɣi si wohia la me.<ref name=AFP2012/> Dɔlelea katã nu tsona zi geɖe ne akladɔ meli o.<ref name=AFP2012/> Akladɔ sesẽ dada ne wodzɔ la toa [[liver transplantion]] me.<ref name=AFP2012/>

<!-- Epidemiology -->
Le xexeame godoo la abe milion 1.5 ƒe dɔlelea ƒe dzesi dzena ƒe sia ƒe<ref name=AFP2012/> eye million akpewo nye dɔa lelawo le wo katã me.<ref name=Was2006>{{cite journal|last=Wasley|first=A|author2=Fiore, A |author3=Bell, BP |title=Hepatitis A in the era of vaccination.|journal=Epidemiol Rev |year=2006|volume=28|pages=101–11|pmid=16775039 |doi=10.1093/epirev/mxj012 |url=http://epirev.oxfordjournals.org/content/28/1/101.long}}</ref> Ebɔ wu le xexeame ƒe akpa siwo medza o eye tsinono nyui hã mesu amewo o.<ref name=WHO2013>{{cite web|title=Hepatitis A Fact sheet N°328|url=http://www.who.int/mediacentre/factsheets/fs328/en/|work=World Health Organization|accessdate=20 February 2014|date=July 2013}}</ref> Le [[developing world]] wome la ɖeviwo si de 90% la le dɔa hafi xɔna ƒe 10 eyata womegalene le tsitsi me o.<ref name=WHO2013/> Edzɔna kpata le dukɔ siwo de ŋgɔ vie la me ne ɖeviwo melee hafi tsi o eye abidodo godoo hã mebɔ o.<ref name=WHO2013/> Le 2010 me la, hepatitis A sesẽ ƒe dodo zu ame 102,000 ku.<ref name=Loz2012>{{cite journal|last=Lozano|first=R|title=Global and regional mortality from 235 causes of death for 20 age groups in 1990 and 2010: a systematic analysis for the Global Burden of Disease Study 2010|journal=Lancet|date=Dec 15, 2012|volume=380|issue=9859|pages=2095–128|pmid=23245604|doi=10.1016/S0140-6736(12)61728-0}}</ref> [[World Hepatitis Day]] vana ƒe sia ƒe le July ƒe ŋkeke 28 dzi be woahe nufiamenyawo tso [[viral hepatitis]] ŋu.<ref name=WHO2013/>

